<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the ShopBuilder you can create a header and a footer. The header and the footer are globally effective for the whole online store.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a header or a footer in the ShopBuilder:</p>
</div>
